name: Simple_Page
tagline: Problem: Design and build a web page in response to the prompt 'something interesting about me.' This will be an opportunity to practice using GitHub as you create a simple site.
body:
### Welcome to My Page!. This page is for my Computer Science class. We are practicing HTML using GitHub. The prompt is to give a short page about myself. ### What do I like doing?

Doing arts and crafts is one of my favorite hobbies. I make various things like key chains, necklace pendants, or little charms. I draw, too!

I am in a Computer Science class (thats why this site is here!). I am also currently learning how to play the piano. ### Other Facts I like the colors jade and blue. I write stories (not often, though). I like pass the time by drawing or listening to music. I write really dark with pencils, it's almost like **I'm writing in bold...** ### ### Support or Contact Having trouble with Pages? Check out our [documentation](https://help.github.com/pages) or [contact support](https://github.com/contact) and weâ€™ll help you sort it out.
